<h2>Booking Confirmed</h2>
<p>Dear <%= user.email %>,</p>
<p>Your equipment booking has been confirmed.</p>
<p>Here are your booking details:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Equipment:</strong> <%= equipment_record.equipment.name %></li>
  <li><strong>Borrow Date:</strong> <%= equipment_record.borrow_date %></li>
  <li><strong>Expected Return Date:</strong> <%= equipment_record.expected_return_date %></li>
  <% if equipment_record.time.present? %>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= equipment_record.time.strftime("%H:%M") %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<p>Thank you for your booking.</p>